snippet.title: When Pigs Fly - Drag Race Challenge Instructions
snippet.description:
Enter the When Pigs Fly Drag Race Challenge!  Top three entries will have their designs included in future updates of the game!

Get more info here: http://gamejolt.com/games/when-pigs-fly/news/when-pigs-fly-drag-race-challenge/42087/
